RACE.FOOTNOTES: UNION FLEET , urged soon after the gate and taken wide, edged up nearing the turn and tracked a contested pace, moved closer past the five sixteenths then bid four wide outside runners entering the lane, took control leaving the three sixteenths, opened up under right handed asking then was geared down the through the final seventy yards. HIGHLAND DREAM stalked the leaders three wide, bid between foes to challenge entering the stretch, failed to kick on with the winner to his outside but continued on willingly for the place. CENTER MID MADDIE sped clear early while two wide, was joined from the inside nearing the half mile marker, dueled around the turn, maintained a tenuous advantage heading to the stretch, could not hold off threats soon into the lane, stayed on past mid stretch then faded. YOUNG TURK drifted in at the break, was corrected and taken to rate a bit, moved up to the inside of the leader heading to the half mile pole, vied under coaxing around the turn, failed to stay on entering the lane and gave way. FORTH reared at the break losing all chance, found himself far back and simply galloped around. There was a stewards' inquiry into the start of FORTH but no action was deemed necessary.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: DEEDS OF LOVE edged up to the inside of rivals early on and contested the pace, was deftly rated back off the leaders into the turn, was coaxed along to hold a forward spot along the rail past the five sixteenths, eased out in upper stretch, closed between runners to take command inside the sixteenth pole and drew clear under a drive. MARIA FROM MIAMI rated forwardly behind foes, was guided three wide past the three eighths, angled four wide into the lane, ranged up to threaten outside foes past the sixteenth pole, failed to match strides with the winner but kept on willingly. MAMA'S EYES , three deep and with the pace nearing the half mile pole, prompted outside SIX THE HARD WAY mid turn, was roused clear in upper stretch, shifted in a bit, failed to contain rivals past the sixteenth marker and weakened. SIX THE HARD WAY , fractious in the post parade, was sent up early and put a head in front between rivals, emerged in a battle to the inside of MAMA'S EYES leaving the far turn, stayed on to about mid stretch then faded. GOLDIENESS dropped off the early pace, came wide for the drive and lacked a solid run. SOLVING PROGRESS dropped back off the early pace while saving ground, shifted out past the three sixteenths and offered a belated response. ELLIE VICTORINA broke slowly, saved ground under asking into the stretch but came up empty. CALM N COLLECTED drafted back off the leaders in the opening furlong then failed to generate a run.
